Database Search for Published Studies An information specialist searched the Medline and EM-
BASE databases for all potentially relevant English language scientific papers published between 1 January 1999 and 31 March 2005, reporting original research on live rats, mice and non-human primates (referred to hereafter as ‘primates’) carried out in publicly funded research establishments in the UK and the USA. (See supplementary online information for search terms).

